UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Level 80',`text_loc2`='Congratulations on your conviction to reach the 80th season of adventure. You are undoubtedly dedicated to the cause of ridding Azeroth of the evils which have plagued us.$B$BAnd while the journey thus far has been no minor feat, the true battle lies ahead.$B$BFight on!$B$BRhonin' WHERE `entry`=13;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='You\'ve Been Around!',`text_loc2`='Well, look at ye!$B$BAnd I thought I had seen some things in this icy place! It seems obvious to this dwarf that you have the fire of the explorer burning in your eyes.$B$BWear this tabard with pride. That way your friends will know who to ask for directions when the time comes!$B$BKeep on the move!$B$B-Brann Bronzebeard' WHERE `entry`=45;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `text_loc2`='War rages throughout our lands. Only the bravest heroes dare challenge strike the Horde where it hurts them most. You are among such heroes.$B$BThe blows you have delivered to the leadership of the Horde will open the door for our final assault. The Horde will bow down to the might of the Alliance.$B$BYour deeds will not go unrewarded. Ride on proudly!$B$B--Your King' WHERE `entry`=614;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `text_loc2`='In this time of great turmoil true heroes rise from the misery. You are one such great hero.$B$BWar is upon us. Your efforts will further our cause on Azeroth. Your great feats shall go rewarded. Take this prize of Orgrimmar and ride to glory.$B$BFor the Horde!$B$BWarchief Thrall' WHERE `entry`=619;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Brutally Dedicated',`text_loc2`='I\'ve been watching you, kid.$B$BYou\'ve got quite a knack for throwing down in that arena. Keep this. Wear it with pride. Now get back in there and show them how it\'s done!$B$BUncle Sal' WHERE `entry`=876;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Quite the Achiever',`text_loc2`='I couldn\'t help but notice what a fine collection of Tabards you\'ve managed to collect over the seasons. You might as well add this one to your collection. It\'s simply been gathering dust in my wardrobe.' WHERE `entry`=1021;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Stinker\'s New Home',`text_loc2`='I\'ve heard how well you take care of our furry friends. I hope you don\'t mind but I must get Stinker a new home. He just refuses to play nice with others.$B$BPlease make sure to feed him twice a day. And um... he has a thing for black cats.$B$B--Breanni' WHERE `entry`=1250;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Greetings from Darnassus',`text_loc2`='Your accomplishments have been profound and far-reaching. Azeroth, with all of the recent turmoil, benefits greatly from those who seek to rid the land of evil.$B$BOnly those who take the time to know our lands understand the sacrifices of the fallen and the valor of our heroes. You are one such hero. Hopefully, you will recant the tales of your adventures for years to come.$B$BOn behalf of the Alliance, I thank you, Loremaster.' WHERE `entry`=1681;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Higher Learning',`text_loc2`='Congratulations on completing$B$Byour studies on The Schools of$B$BArcane Magic. In recognition of your$B$Bdedication. I\'m enclosing this special$B$Bvolume completing the series.$B$BI believe you\'ll find this tome$B$Bparticularly entertaining. But I\'ll$B$Bleave that for your discovery.$B$BSincerely,$B$BRhonin' WHERE `entry`=1956;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='The Coin Master',`text_loc2`='Greetings and congratulations on collecting the full set of Dalaran coins! As a reward for all your hard work I have enclosed a freshly minted Titanium Seal of Dalaran. This is a special coin that we only grant to the most ardent of collectors.$B$BI hope you enjoy this special reward. You\'ve earned it!$B$BSincerely,$B$BJepetto Joybuzz' WHERE `entry`=2096;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Glory of the Hero',`text_loc2`='Champion,$B$BWord has traveled to Wyrmrest Temple$B$Bof the great heroic deeds you have$B$Baccomplished since arriving in$B$BNorthrend.$B$BYour bravery should not go$B$Bunrecognized. Please accept this gift$B$Bon behalf of the Aspects. Together we$B$Bshall rid Azeroth of evil, once and for$B$Beternity.$B$BAlexstrasza the Life-Binder' WHERE `entry`=2136;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Leading the Cavalry',`text_loc2`='I couldn\'t help but to notice how good you are with the livestock. With all the activity around here, business has been better than ever for me. I don\'t suppose you\'d mind looking after this Albino Drake for me? I simply don\'t have enough spare minutes in the day to care for all of these animals.$B$BYours,$BMei' WHERE `entry`=2143;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='What A Long, Strange Trip It\'s Been',`text_loc2`='With the drums of war pounding in the distance, it is easy for the denizens of Azeroth to forget all that life has to offer. You, on the other hand, have maintained the dignity of the good races of Azeroth with your ability to remeber what we fight for. To not celebrate our victories is another form of defeat. Remeber that well, reveler. May others be inspired by your good cheer, Alexstrasza the Life-Binder' WHERE `entry`=2144;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='What A Long, Strange Trip It\'s Been',`text_loc2`='With the drums of war pounding in the distance, it is easy for the denizens of Azeroth to forget all that life has to offer. You, on the other hand, have maintained the dignity of the good races of Azeroth with your ability to remeber what we fight for. To not celebrate our victories is another form of defeat. Remeber that well, reveler. May others be inspired by your good cheer, Alexstrasza the Life-Binder' WHERE `entry`=2145;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Lil\' Game Hunter',`text_loc2`='Hello!$B$BI understand you\'ve managed to give even that mischievous Stinker a warm and loving home... I was hoping you might consider taking in another wayward orphan?$B$BThis little fawn is a shy one, but you\'ll have no trouble winning her friendship with the enclosed: her favorite salt lick!$B$B--Breanni' WHERE `entry`=2516;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Mountain o\' Mounts',`text_loc2`='I\'ve heard your stables are nearly as extensive as mine, now. Impressive! Perhaps we can help one another...$B$BI\'ve one too many dragonhawks, and hoped you could give this one a home. Naturally it\'s been trained as a mount and not a hunting pet, and you\'ll find it as loyal and tireless as any other steed I raise.$B$BYours again,$BMei' WHERE `entry`=2536;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Mountain o\' Mounts',`text_loc2`='I\'ve heard your stables are nearly as extensive as mine, now. Impressive! Perhaps we can help one another...$B$BI\'ve one too many dragonhawks, and hoped you could give this one a home. Naturally it\'s been trained as a mount and not a hunting pet, and you\'ll find it as loyal and tireless as any other steed I raise.$B$BYours again,$BMei' WHERE `entry`=2537;
UPDATE `locales_achievement_reward` SET `subject_loc2`='Glory of the Ulduar Raider',`text_loc2`='Dear $N,$B$BI hope ye\'re doing well and that ye\'ve had time to recover from our shenanigans in Ulduar$B$BMe lads from the prospecting team happened upon this poor \'alf dead riding-drake hatchling. Must\'ve been an Iron Dwarf experiment of some sort.$B$BWe\'ve patched him back to health and you\'ll find he\'s not so wee anymore! None of us knows much about riding anything but rams and pack mules and since we owed ye one for what ye did back there... We thought perhaps you\'d accept him as a gift.$B$BYours,$BBrann Bronzebeard' WHERE `entry`=2957;
